name: No. 6 (Blue Panes In Deep Blue)
description:
Part of a collection of hand-made color field items, this piece is a doorway to the Third dimension.

The glowing Blue light that transpires from four horizontal panes invites the soul of the viewer to walk through and call to the inner Self through the liminal gateway. 

It is the space of deep meditation where the mental and physical blend with the spiritual dimension in an unending stream of sensations, images, feelings, and thoughts.
